   by Jack Canfield, Mark Victor Hansen, Patty Aubery and
</P>
<P>
   Nancy Mitchell Autio. (Health Communications, $12.95.)
</P>
<P>
   Inspiration. (b)
</P>
<P>
   THE CARBOHYDRATE ADDICT'S DIET, by Rachael F. Heller ... 3 ...
26
</P>
<P>
