<HEADLINE>
GETTING IT WRONG IN A PHOTO CAPTION 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
 By FOX BUTTERFIELD with KARI HASKELL   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
