<SLUG> BC-R-SATELLITE-SECRECY-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SNOOPING'S NOT JUST FOR SPIES ANYMORE 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
(ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Nonsubscribers can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036
or 888-346-9867.) 
 By WILLIAM J. BROAD   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
