<HEADLINE>
DIGITAL DIN: THE GOLDEN AGE OF TECHNO-BORES 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
 By AMY HARMON   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
