across racial lines than youngsters. Why is that? And what are the
other racial divides? I've got research material from Nielsen (Top
10 or 20 from black and white favorites, top choices from black and
white teens and over-50s, etc.) and comments from an expert analyst
at media buyer BBDO New York who comments on the latest trend.
(Holloway, Austin American-Statesman). MOVED
</P>
<P>
   NEWSSTAND _ Periodicals on the newsstands this week. (O'Briant,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
