<DOCNO> NYT20000424.0195 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-24 14:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5701 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a BC-HMONG-LAOS-ECONOMIST-     04-24 0922
