<HEADLINE>
THREE MINUTES THAT SHOOK AMERICA _ AND GORE'S CHANCES    
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This 775-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)     
