<TEXT>
<P>
   Editors, in addition to those stories listed on the
AM-NYT-BUDGET, AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET, BC-PAGE1-CONSIDER,
BC-EARLY-FRONTPAGE and BC-FINFRONTS, these stories will also move
