(888) 346-9867; e-mail: patryan(at)nytimes.com.
</P>
<P>
   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   (Will move in the ``i'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   TIMOR-SOLDIERS (Liquica, East Timor) _ It is an extraordinary
moment here, with hundreds of the men who brutalized their country
last September trickling back from their refuge in Indonesian West
Timor to beg forgiveness from the survivors. By Seth Mydans.
</P>
<P>
   With map.
</P>
